#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:426
msgid "Adjust Output Quality"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:428
msgid ""
"The server supports adjusting output quality and compression levels for both "
"image and video generation through the `output-quality` and `output-"
"compression` parameters."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:430
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:432
msgid ""
"**`output-quality`** (string, optional): Preset quality level that "
"automatically sets compression. **Default is `\"default\"`**. Valid values:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:433
msgid "`\"maximum\"`: Highest quality (100)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:434
msgid "`\"high\"`: High quality (90)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:435
msgid "`\"medium\"`: Medium quality (55)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:436
msgid "`\"low\"`: Lower quality (35)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:437
msgid ""
"`\"default\"`: Auto-adjust based on media type (50 for video, 75 for image)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:439
msgid ""
"**`output-compression`** (integer, optional): Direct compression level "
"override (0-100). **Default is `None`**. When provided (not `None`), takes "
"precedence over `output-quality`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:440
msgid "`0`: Lowest quality, smallest file size"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:441
msgid "`100`: Highest quality, largest file size"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:443
msgid "Notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:445
msgid ""
"**Precedence**: When both `output-quality` and `output-compression` are "
"provided, `output-compression` takes precedence"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:446
msgid ""
"**Format Support**: Quality settings apply to JPEG, and video formats. PNG "
"uses lossless compression and ignores these settings"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/api/openai_api.md:447
msgid ""
"**File Size vs Quality**: Lower compression values (or \"low\" quality "
"preset) produce smaller files but may show visible artifacts"
msgstr ""
